---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const LAST_UPDATED = 'July 4, 2026';
const CONTACT_EMAIL = 'hello@tokyoinseason.com';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for Tokyo in Season: what data we collect, how the newsletter works, and your rights under GDPR."
  ogType="website"
>
  <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl text-sumi mb-2 leading-tight">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="text-warm-gray-mid text-sm mb-12">Last updated {LAST_UPDATED}</p>

  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none font-serif text-sumi leading-relaxed space-y-6">

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-sumi mt-10 mb-4 not-prose">What we collect</h2>
    <p>
      When you sign up for our free newsletter, we collect the email address you provide through
      the signup form. We don't collect any other personal information on this site — there are
      no accounts, and we don't track you individually for advertising purposes.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-sumi mt-10 mb-4 not-prose">Why we collect it</h2>
    <p>
      Your email address is used solely to send you the free guide you requested and, if you
      remain subscribed, occasional newsletter updates — new venue openings, price changes, and
      what's genuinely worth booking. We do not sell, rent, or share your email address with
      third parties for their own marketing.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-sumi mt-10 mb-4 not-prose">Who processes it</h2>
    <p>
      Newsletter signups and delivery are handled by{' '}
      <a href="https://buttondown.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-matcha underline">Buttondown</a>,
      our email service provider. Buttondown stores your email address on our behalf and sends
      emails to you when we publish an update. You can review Buttondown's own privacy practices
      on their website.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-sumi mt-10 mb-4 not-prose">Unsubscribing</h2>
    <p>
      Every email we send includes an unsubscribe link. Clicking it removes you from the list
      immediately — no need to contact us first, though you're welcome to.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-sumi mt-10 mb-4 not-prose">Affiliate links and cookies</h2>
    <p>
      Some links on this site are affiliate links (including links to GetYourGuide and Klook).
      Clicking one of these links may set a cookie on the destination platform's site so that,
      if you book, the platform can attribute the booking to us and pay a commission. We don't
      control these cookies directly — they're set by the platform you're redirected to, subject
      to that platform's own privacy policy. See our{' '}
      <a href="/disclaimer" class="text-matcha underline">Disclaimer</a> for more on our affiliate
      relationships.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-sumi mt-10 mb-4 not-prose">Your rights (GDPR)</h2>
    <p>
      If you're located in the European Economic Area or UK, you have the right to access the
      personal data we hold about you, request that we correct or delete it, and object to or
      restrict how we use it. Since the only data we hold is your email address and subscription
      status, most requests are handled by simply unsubscribing or asking us to delete your
      record. To make a request, contact us at{' '}
      <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`} class="text-matcha underline">{CONTACT_EMAIL}</a> and
      we'll respond within a reasonable time.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-sumi mt-10 mb-4 not-prose">Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions about this policy or your data can be sent to{' '}
      <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`} class="text-matcha underline">{CONTACT_EMAIL}</a>.
    </p>

  </div>

  <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-warm-gray">
    <p class="text-sm">
      <a href="/disclaimer" class="text-matcha hover:underline">Disclaimer →</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
